        <item>
            <title>NVIDIA 2025 CES 黄仁勋演讲透视： 老板们留意，企业将有 7 大改变</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/07/ai-enterpise/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ai-enterpise</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/07/ai-enterpise/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[天恩]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 11:12:41 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Unwire Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285642</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在今年的 CES 2025 上，NVIDIA 创办人黄仁勋展示了多项革命性技术，这些技术正在深刻改变企业的运营模式，从生产效率到成本控制，再到开拓全新市场。以下将从企业老板的角度，详细解释这些技术如何帮助企业应对未来挑战，并提供更多实际应用场景，以激发灵感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285662" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-33-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-33-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-33-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285669" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-40-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-40-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-40-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>模拟店舖或仓「未来」 降低运营成本</h2><p>NVIDIA 在 CES 2025 上展示的 Digital Twin 技术为企业提供了全新经营工具。透过虚拟世界模拟现实运作，企业可以预测并解决潜在问题，同时改善整体流程。以货仓管理为例，Digital Twin 技术能模拟高峰期的物流运作，测试不同货架设计和物流路线，确保操作流畅。制造业也能透过模拟生产线排程，加强资源更灵活使用。Nvidia 分享了与 Keon 和 Accenture 的合作，展示了如何使用 Omniverse Digital Twin 模拟仓库运营，模拟日常和季节性需求变化、空间限制和机器人系统的整合。这些模拟帮助企业在部署前预测关键 KPI（如吞吐量和效率），以降低风险并提升运营表现​。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285674" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-45-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-45-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-45-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285658" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-29-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-29-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-29-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285659" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-30-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-30-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-30-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>极大量数据分析，决策不靠「直觉」</h2><p>传统依赖经验或直觉的决策方式，面对市场快速变化时往往捉襟见肘。NVIDIA 展示的 AI 技术改变了这一现状。它能分析大量历史数据，结合即时市场资讯，为企业提供更准确的预测与决策支持。</p><p>零售商也能通过 AI 预测不同促销方案的效果。模拟数据显示，某项促销活动可能在北美市场更受欢迎，而在欧洲市场效果较差，企业因此可以提前优化投放策略，避免不必要的资源浪费。</p><p>AI 的核心价值在于它能从大量数据中提取洞察，帮助企业做出基于事实的决策，提升应变能力，并降低因错误决策带来的损失。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285673" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-44-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-44-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-44-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285672" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-43-694x577.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="577" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-43-694x577.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-43-scaled.jpg 1083w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2></h2><h2>节能增效，实现环保目标</h2><p>能源消耗已成为企业运营中的主要挑战，尤其是随著数据运算需求的快速增长。NVIDIA 的最新 GPU 技术提供了革命性解决方案，Blackwell GPU 每瓦性能提高四倍，不只满足高效运算需求，还能显著降低能源开支。</p><p>举例来说，一家大型金融机构可以通过升级新的 Blackwell GPU ，有望将高频交易系统的延迟减少 30%，同时将数据中心的能耗降低 25%。这不仅能帮助企业节省大量成本，还能实现碳中和目标，满足越来越多投资者对 ESG（环境、社会与治理）的要求。</p><p>此外，这项技术对需要大量数据处理的行业，例如医疗诊断和科研，将带来巨大的帮助。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285660" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-31-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-31-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-31-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>灵活资源使用，降低 AI 技术门槛</h2><p>NVIDIA 推出的 AI Token 模式，为企业提供了一种按需使用资源的灵活方案。企业无需购买昂贵硬件，只需根据实际需求支付费用，这对于中小企和初创企业尤其有吸引力。<br />
想像一家初创生物科技公司，它需要进行复杂的基因序列分析，但日常运算需求较低。通过 AI Token，这家公司可以在项目高峰期快速扩展计算能力，而在日常运营中保持低成本运行。这种按需模式大大降低了技术门槛，让中小企业也能负担得起尖端的 AI 计算资源。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285668" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-39-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-39-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-39-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285675" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-46-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-46-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-46-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>AI Agent 数码员工节省人力资源</h2><p>NVIDIA 推出的 AI Agent 技术，让「数码员工」成为可能。AI 代理可以处理大量重复性任务，例如客服查询、报表生成和市场数据分析，帮助企业解放人力资源，专注于更高价值的工作。NVIDIA 预测未来  30  亿知识工作者将拥有 AI 助理，这些助理可以协助完成高效的任务，例如：<br />
自动生成财务报告及协助研究人员设计和筛选数十亿化合物，加速新药开发​。<br />
​</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285665" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-36-694x554.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="554" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-36-694x554.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-36-scaled.jpg 1128w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285663" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-34-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-34-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-34-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>开放平台推动定制化创新</h2><p>NVIDIA 的开放式平台让企业能够快速开发符合自身需求的 AI 应用，从金融到医疗，再到教育与零售，各行各业均能受益。例如医疗机构利用 AI 提高诊断准确率，而零售商则采用 AI 技术实现个性化推荐，增强顾客购物体验。</p><p>例如，一家高端零售品牌开发了 AI 驱动的个性化推荐系统，能根据消费者的购物习惯和喜好进行精准推荐，结果显示销售额提升了 20%。这种客制化的 AI 应用不仅提升了用户体验，还帮助企业打开了新的收入来源。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285666" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-37-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-37-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-37-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>企业必需注意 「 AI 责任」</h2><p>在推动 AI 技术应用的同时，数据安全与算法伦理成为企业不得不重视的议题。例如一家医疗机构定期审查其 AI 诊断算法，确保公平性与可靠性。一家电商平台则通过数据加密措施，加强用户隐私保护，进一步赢得市场信任。</p><p>企业在享受 AI 技术带来的效率提升之际，也需承担起社会责任，确保技术的应用符合伦理和法律规范，从而实现可持续发展。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285661" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-32-694x441.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="441" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-32-694x441.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-32.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285667" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-38-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-38-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nvidiaceojensenhuang-38-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>结语：企业及早 AI 化「保命」</h2><p>NVIDIA 展示的创新技术，从 Digital Twin 到 AI Token 已经不再是未来的构想，而是可以即时落地的实用工具。这些技术为企业提供了提升效率、降低成本的全新方法，帮助他们在市场变化中保持竞争力。</p><p>企业应该从小规模试点开始，逐步扩展应用，并投资于数据基础设施和技术人才培养，为数码转型做好准备。抓住科技浪潮，现在就是行动的最佳时机，因为今天的决策将决定未来的格局。</p><p><strong>声明</strong>：文中提到的具体数据和案例基于 NVIDIA 技术的公开信息以及行业趋势推测，目的是帮助读者理解技术的应用潜力，并非 NVIDIA 演讲中提到的实际数据。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_71972"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/k82RwXqZHY8?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/07/ai-enterpise/ai/">NVIDIA 2025 CES 黄仁勋演讲透视： 老板们留意，企业将有 7 大改变</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
