            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285563</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Elon Musk 日前宣布调整 X（前身为 Twitter）演算法，将优先推广「有教育意义、具资讯性／有趣的」帖文，此举引发社会关注平台是否将加强内容审查。部分网友认为此举为「言论审查」，激起民愤。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">Algorithm tweak coming soon to promote more informational/entertaining content. We will publish the changes to <a href="https://twitter.com/XEng?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@XEng</a>.</p><p>Our goal is to maximize unregretted user-seconds. Too much negativity is being pushed that technically grows user time, but not unregretted user time.</p><p>— Elon Musk (@elonmusk) <a href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1875355425601999255?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">January 4, 2025</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>新演算法将使 X 推荐更加正面积极的内容，并减少负面情绪及争议性讯息。Elon Musk 指，目前 X 平台的经常推荐争议性强的内容，这类内容虽能带来较高的点击率及互动，但也会引发大量的负面反应。他期望更新演算法后能使平台的内容呈现更多正向、有建设性的讯息。</p><p>尽管 Elon Musk 希望改善平台氛围，但该决定遭到部分用户强烈反对。批评者认为，调整后的演算法将加强监控内容，从而影响平台的中立性及言论自由。更有声音指新演算法可能会过度审查某些特定议题，例如与政治或社会相关的敏感内容。是次 Elon Musk 调整演算法引发网民质疑如何判断「何谓负面内容」，并表示这样的改动会压制有异于主流观点的声音，削弱 X 的开放性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285580" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010723104-694x366.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="366" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010723104-694x366.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010723104.jpg 893w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://abmedia.io/elon-musk-edit-twitter-algorithm">Abmeda</a>、<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2025/1/4/24335699/elon-musk-says-xs-algorithm-pushes-too-much-negativity">The Verge</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/07/elon-musk-algorithm-x-edited/life-tech/social-network/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
